title: Episode 62: Western Adventures, Christian Movies & Evangelistic Atheists
description: Skye is back in  town!  We hear about his travels out west, then the group careens wildly through this week's stories about Christian movies, heaven, the end times, evangelistic atheists and, of course, gay rights.  Buckle up for the ride!
